\c 14
\s Ukubusa kukaAsa
\p
\v 1 UAbhiya waselala laboyise, bamngcwabela emzini kaDavida. UAsa indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe. Ensukwini zakhe ilizwe laba lokuthula iminyaka elitshumi\x + 1 Kho. 15.8.\x*.
\v 2 UAsa wasesenza okuhle lokulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe.
\v 3 Ngoba wasusa amalathi awemzini lendawo eziphakemeyo\x + 15.17. 14.5. 1 Kho. 15.14.\x*, wadiliza insika eziyizithombe, wagamula izixuku\x + Dute. 7.5. 1 Kho. 16.33.\x*.
\v 4 Wasesithi kuJuda kabayidinge iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, lokuthi bagcine umthetho lomlayo.
\v 5 Wasesusa kuyo yonke imizi yakoJuda indawo eziphakemeyo lamalathi okutshisela impepha. Lombuso waba lokuthula phambi kwakhe\x + 15.17. 14.5. 1 Kho. 15.14.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Wasesakha imizi ebiyelweyo koJuda, ngoba ilizwe lalilokuthula\x + 11.5.\x*, njalo kungelampi laye ngaleyominyaka, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yamphumuza\x + 14.1.\x*.
\v 7 Wasesithi kuJuda: Asiyakheni limizi, si\add yi\add*zingelezele ngemiduli, lemiphotshongo, amasango, lemigoqo, ilizwe lisesephambi kwethu\x + 8.5.\x*; ngoba siyidingile iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, si\add yi\add*dingile, yasinika ukuthula inhlangothi zonke. Basebesakha, baphumelela\x + 15.15. 20.30.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo uAsa wayelebutho labazinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amathathu abavela koJuda, bethwele ihawu lomkhonto, labazinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili abavela koBhenjamini\x + 13.3.\x* bethwele isihlangu esikhulu benyathela idandili; bonke laba babengamaqhawe alamandla\x + 1 Lan. 5.18.\x*.
\p
\v 9 UZera umEthiyophiya\x + 16.8. 12.3.\x* wasephuma ukumelana labo elebutho eliyinkulungwane yezinkulungwane lezinqola ezingamakhulu amathathu, wasefika eMaresha\x + Josh. 15.44. 11.8.\x*.
\v 10 UAsa wasephuma ukumelana laye, bahlela impi esihotsheni seZefatha\x + Hlu. 1.17.\x* eMaresha\x + 11.8. Josh. 15.44.\x*.
\v 11 UAsa wasekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 13.14. Eks. 14.10. 1 Lan. 5.20. Hlab. 22.5. Hlu. 3.9.\x* wathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, kakusilutho kuwe ukunceda, loba kwabanengi loba kwabangelamandla; sisize, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wethu\x + 1 Sam. 14.6. Hlu. 7.7.\x*, ngoba seyeme kuwe\x + 13.18.\x*; njalo ngebizo lakho sizemelana lalelixuku; N\nd kosi\nd*, wena unguNkulunkulu wethu\x + 1 Sam. 17.45.\x*; umuntu kangakwehluli\x + 1 Lan. 29.14.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yawatshaya amaEthiyophiya\f + \fk amaKushi: \fl Heb. \fq amaKhushi.\f* phambi kukaAsa laphambi kukaJuda; amaEthiyophiya asebaleka\x + 13.15.\x*.
\v 13 UAsa labantu ababelaye baxotshana lawo kwaze kwaba seGerari\x + Gen. 10.19. 20.1. 26.1,6.\x*; kwasekusiwa kumaEthiyophiya okokuthi kakwaze kwaba lokuvuseleleka kiwo, ngoba acotshodiswa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* laphambi kwebutho layo. Basebemuka lempango enengi kakhulu\x + Ezra 9.8,9.\x*.
\v 14 Basebetshaya yonke imizi ezingelezele iGerari\x + Gen. 10.19. 20.1. 26.1,6.\x*, ngoba uvalo lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaluphezu kwayo. Basebephanga yonke imizi, ngoba kwakulempango enengi kiyo\x + 17.10. 20.29. Gen. 35.5.\x*.
\v 15 Basebetshaya lamathente ezifuyo, bathumba izimvu ezinengi lamakamela, babuyela eJerusalema.
